**Persona Files: `personas/{name}.yml`**
```yaml
# ~/.mame/personas/default.yml
name: "Mame-Mini"
soul: "SOUL-Mame.md"              # Path relative to MAME_HOME
language: "en"

models:
  default: "openrouter/minimax/minimax-m2.7"
  heartbeat: "google/gemini-3.1-flash-lite-preview"
  complex: "openrouter/deepseek/deepseek-r1"    # Optional

